nodes.text: A droid battalion was dispatched by Supreme Martial Commander General Grievous to reinforce one of the Separatist Alliance's outposts on Felucia. Battle droids of the battalion arrived in a C-9979 landing craft and fell under the command of TZ-33. Shortly after deploying, the outpost was attacked by the 104th Battalion, the 501st Legion, and clone tank divisions. The Galactic Republic forces quickly destroyed the Separatist forces.
